            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Manib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Monim<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> Cesti <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>et Servill<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> uxsori <note>sic</note> <lb n="4"/>su<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> et fili<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> et alter<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="5"/>filli<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> vocatur <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>NA <lb n="0"/>IMPR<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Dis Manib(us) / monimentum / Cesti[(a)e?] [Grat?]ill(a)e uxsori / su(a)[e] et fili(a)e et alter(i) / [fi]li(a)e qu(a)e vocatur [---]. Grabmonument mit Abbildung von 3 Personen. Textende: et altera(e) / filli(a)e qu(a)e vocatur [--] nachträglich hinzugefügt; im Inschriftfeld rechts erscheinen die Buchstaben [---]na / impr[---]; wohl Fortsetzung des Textes; Namen in Z.2.: Monime oder Monima, Cestus oder Cestius. L als griechischer Buchstabe.</p>
            </div>
